OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTo sing or not to sing?    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FTheatre etiquette in the   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fspotlight                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Should you be allowed to sing along at 
OL,6, a musical? After unwanted crowd        
OL,7, participation led to The Bodyguard     
OL,8, being cut short and police being       
OL,9, called, the issue of audience behaviour
OL,10, - especially since the pandemic - has  
OL,11, been thrust into the spotlight.        
OL,13,F"Please refrain from singing along."   
OL,15,FThose words greet audiences on posters 
OL,16,Fon the doors of Manchester's Palace    
OL,17,FTheatre, and inside the foyers.        
OL,19,FSinging along at a musical might not   
OL,20,Fsound like a big issue. It's often part
OL,21,Fof the fun.                            
